column2: SELECT ts.SystemStudentID StudentID, e.GradeLevel, ts.SchoolYear4Digit, ts.TestPeriod, ts.TestSubjectGroup, #, ts.TestType, ts.TestScore FROM Enrollment e INNER JOIN TestScores ts ON e.SystemStudentID = ts.SystemStudentID INNER JOIN ParentEngagement pe ON pe.StudentID = ts.SystemStudentID INNER JOIN EmotionalScreener es ON es.StudentID = pe.StudentID union all SELECT ts.SystemStudentID StudentID, e.GradeLevel, pe.SchoolYear4Digit, CONVERT (int, #) , #, # , #, # FROM Enrollment e INNER JOIN TestScores ts ON e.SystemStudentID = ts.SystemStudentID INNER JOIN ParentEngagement pe ON pe.StudentID = ts.SystemStudentID INNER JOIN EmotionalScreener es ON es.StudentID = pe.StudentID union all SELECT ts.SystemStudentID StudentID, e.GradeLevel, es.SchoolYear4Digit, es.Period, #, #, #, es.Score FROM Enrollment e INNER JOIN TestScores ts ON e.SystemStudentID = ts.SystemStudentID INNER JOIN ParentEngagement pe ON pe.StudentID = ts.SystemStudentID INNER JOIN EmotionalScreener es ON es.StudentID = pe.StudentID
